About us
New-Design Biotechnology was founded by Shawn and Zeus in Guangzhou, China in 2013. We are an innovative technology enterprise focusing on the home medical health supplies industry, integrating design, research & development, production, sales& service. We have the entire industrial chain product planning, development, manufacturing, wholesale and retail construction capabilities. At the same time, we are also a national high-tech enterprise and hold many core patented technologies.
Our factory covers 20,000 square meter with injection and mold workshop. Daily capacity can reach 3000 sets of products. We have 10 product series mainly, which are moxibustion Instrument Series , Infrared Protective Gear Series, Traditional moxibustion Series , Massage Series , Electric Heating Series , Correction Series, Plaster Series , Home Care Series, Private Care Series , Medical Beauty Series. Meanwhile, we set up very strict product quality control through DQE, SQE, FQC, and CQE these four aspects to manage. In addition, we have self-established laboratory inspection and invite official organization inspect. Because we trust that quality improvement comes from continual pursuit of details.
